Bez nasiona piawki stoja glodne na 91.2%.
Prosimy usilnie " Please seed, we want to finish our intake ! "
Dziekujemy slicznie.

Hi Celerion !
A week after. You had 11 leeches, 9 from Poland. You lost them all. If you don't know how to seed, just ask in here. Choice of Polish, French and English, take your pick.
